column16: Jesus Guzman singles on a line drive to center fielder Tony Campana.
Jason Bartlett flies out to right fielder Tyler Colvin.
Will Venable grounds out, second baseman Darwin Barney to first baseman Carlos Pena.
Juan Francisco grounds out to first baseman Jeff Baker.    Yonder Alonso scores.    Devin Mesoraco to 3rd.
Devin Mesoraco doubles (2) on a ground ball to left fielder Tony Campana.    Yonder Alonso to 3rd.
Jay Bruce flies out to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
Joey Votto grounds out, first baseman Jeff Baker to pitcher John Gaub.
